data.description: Located in Bentwood Country Club, absolutely stunning 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath, 2 car garage home features a show stopping fireplace, picture windows, plantation wood shutters, tile flooring in the common areas, and granite throughout. Fully sodded, irrigation system front and back and privacy fenced. Additional 1100 square feet of concrete patio outback with two pergolas and hot tub for relaxing evenings.
data.whatILove: Plantation Shutters, picture windows, large walk-in pantry, open floor plan, extra large corner lot and covered patio. Watching the deer in the neighborhood every evening is an added bonus.
